Package: emane
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: EMANE is an Extendable Mobile Ad-hoc Network Emulator that allows for heterogeneous network emulation using a pluggable MAC and PHY layer architecture.

